She's scared.
You're scaring her!

37:00.967 --> 37:02.718
-[banging stops]
-[breathing heavily]

37:02.802 --> 37:04.511
[breathing heavily]

37:05.304 --> 37:06.973
[breathing heavily]

37:11.310 --> 37:13.187
[footsteps receding]

37:16.315 --> 37:18.150
[beeping steadies]

37:21.362 --> 37:22.738
[mouthing] Shh.

37:38.004 --> 37:39.338
[exhales heavily]

37:40.339 --> 37:41.382
They're gone.

37:41.507 --> 37:43.175
-[bangs on door]
-[Melissa shrieks]

38:03.779 --> 38:05.697
[breathing heavily]

38:05.781 --> 38:07.408
[footsteps receding]

38:20.254 --> 38:21.923
[gasping]

38:22.882 --> 38:24.466
