38:48.282 --> 38:49.992
[Melissa] Would they do that?
Your family, would they--

38:50.076 --> 38:51.743
[Travis] They're not our family.
[Brad] Hey, look at me.

38:51.827 --> 38:53.412
-I'm asking you a question. Who is it?
-Don't touch me.

38:53.495 --> 38:54.914
-What aren't you telling us, Travis?
-Don't touch me.

38:54.997 --> 38:56.248
-I'm asking you a question.
-[Melissa] Stop it!

38:56.332 --> 38:57.624
[Travis] Get off me!
[Melissa] Stop it! Stop it!

39:16.810 --> 39:18.104
[EKG monitor beeps]

39:18.187 --> 39:19.981
-[powering up]
-[Melissa sighs]

39:20.106 --> 39:21.690
[breathing heavily]

39:25.111 --> 39:26.278
[sighs]

39:33.202 --> 39:34.996
[Brad breathing heavily]

39:43.795 --> 39:45.547
[EKG beeping]

40:00.687 --> 40:02.148
[Brad] What the fuck?

40:08.820 --> 40:09.863
{\an8}What do they want?

40:13.159 --> 40:15.077
[Travis] They want us to give her this.

40:28.174 --> 40:29.966
[Brad] They can't get in this room.

40:48.194 --> 40:50.196
Stop.

40:50.279 --> 40:53.199
Travis. Stop it.

40:53.282 --> 40:56.993
