God knows what into her.

41:44.083 --> 41:45.667
It's experimental.
It's not fucking heroin.

41:45.751 --> 41:47.253
Who are we, huh?
We're not doctors.

41:47.336 --> 41:48.670
We're her sons.

41:56.928 --> 41:58.139
It'll work.

42:05.271 --> 42:06.772
[Brad] I know it will.

42:08.607 --> 42:13.069
And when it does...
then what happens?

42:15.030 --> 42:16.157
