[Melissa] No. No.

42:58.199 --> 42:59.783
My room's closer.

43:04.037 --> 43:06.081
No. No, no, no. No, no.
It's too dangerous.

43:06.165 --> 43:07.458
They're gonna
get in this room eventually.

43:11.295 --> 43:12.588
Fuck.

43:12.671 --> 43:14.673
-It's okay.
-No, it's not.

43:16.508 --> 43:18.009
I have to try.

43:20.971 --> 43:22.598
Fuck, man.

43:22.681 --> 43:24.891
Hey. I have to try.

44:05.766 --> 44:08.101
[sighs] Damn it.

44:17.319 --> 44:19.154
[floor creaking]

44:29.831 --> 44:31.041
Shit.

46:00.506 --> 46:02.340
[Melissa] There's Travis.

46:14.185 --> 46:17.398
There you are.
Where's the other guy?

46:22.903 --> 46:24.946
[Brad] What's that right there?
[Melissa] What?

46:25.030 --> 46:26.532
[Brad] There.
[Melissa] Where?

46:26.615 --> 46:27.949
[Melissa screaming]

46:29.868 --> 46:31.703
[Brad and masked man grunting]

46:33.246 --> 46:34.915
[Melissa groans]

46:40.754 --> 46:42.380
[motorbike starting]

46:43.256 --> 46:45.258
-[engine revving]
-[grunts]

46:53.391 --> 46:54.601
[Travis grunts]

47:00.816 --> 47:02.568
[Travis grunting]

47:10.408 --> 47:12.077
[gun cocks]

47:13.787 --> 47:14.788
[Travis groans]

47:18.625 --> 47:20.919
[Brad] No! No!

47:21.002 --> 47:23.254
No!

47:27.092 --> 47:28.927
[church bell tolling]

47:56.830 --> 47:58.832
[church bell continues tolling]

48:04.880 --> 48:06.632
[tolling stops]

