52:18.549 --> 52:20.260
[EKG beeping]

53:19.652 --> 53:21.654
[footsteps thumping]

53:34.835 --> 53:36.002
[both grunting]

53:44.886 --> 53:46.847
[George screams]

53:50.892 --> 53:52.643
[masked man panting]

54:20.171 --> 54:21.839
[creaking]

54:28.679 --> 54:30.098
Come on.

54:42.193 --> 54:43.653
[water flowing]

54:54.539 --> 54:56.207
[wolves howling on TV]

