[upbeat music playing on TV]

55:03.339 --> 55:05.758
[man on TV] <i>Step by step,</i>
<i>as the mill prospered...</i>

55:05.883 --> 55:07.885
-[sighs]
<i>-...the farmers got more money.</i>

55:08.011 --> 55:10.138
<i>Until they,</i>
<i>like the miller and his helpers,</i>

55:10.221 --> 55:13.266
<i>could buy automobiles</i>
<i>and radios and electric...</i>

55:13.391 --> 55:17.562
<i>...and the other conveniences</i>
<i>to make farm life easier and happier.</i>

55:25.903 --> 55:28.114
<i>Today, in industry,</i>
<i>the money invested...</i>

55:28.239 --> 55:30.283
[man on TV continues speaking
