55:36.539 --> 55:40.251
<i>...make it possible for him</i>
<i>to produce more and thus to earn more.</i>

55:40.376 --> 55:44.380
<i>No wonder the American workman</i>
<i>has become the highest paid in the world,</i>

55:44.464 --> 55:47.383
<i>with the greatest amount of leisure time.</i>

55:47.467 --> 55:51.346
<i>No wonder, too, that we consumers</i>
<i>have benefited through the production</i>

55:51.429 --> 55:55.058
<i>of continually better goods</i>
<i>at lower prices.</i>

55:55.141 --> 55:56.809
<i>Yet it all seems so natural...</i>

55:56.934 --> 55:58.269
[T.J. sighs]

