<i>Hello, and thank you for choosing to learn</i>
<i>more about the New Life Church</i>

56:29.634 --> 56:33.388
<i>where worship and devotion,</i>
<i>both to Christ and our fellow members,</i>

56:33.471 --> 56:36.641
<i>serve as the foundation of our belief.</i>

56:36.766 --> 56:38.893
<i>At the New Life Church,</i>

56:38.976 --> 56:42.480
<i>we cherish the opportunity</i>
<i>to serve the Lord as part of his flock.</i>

56:42.605 --> 56:48.194
<i>But we also consider ourselves shepherds</i>
<i>in our own right,</i>

56:48.319 --> 56:50.071
<i>dutifully protecting one another</i>

56:50.155 --> 56:53.324
<i>from the wolves of the world</i>
<i>who might wish to prey upon us.</i>

56:53.991 --> 56:57.245
<i>Our parishioners include</i>
<i>lawyers and doctors</i>

56:57.328 --> 56:59.789
<i>and school teachers, young and old.</i>

56:59.872 --> 57:04.585
<i>All races and backgrounds,</i>
<i>people from all walks of life.</i>

57:04.669 --> 57:07.588
<i>We are all the same in the eyes of God.</i>

57:07.672 --> 57:12.009
<i>Each of us is special.</i>
<i>And so are you.</i>

57:12.135 --> 57:15.388
<i>So join me now</i>
<i>for a more in-depth look at...</i>

57:15.513 --> 57:17.098
[Grace groans]

57:17.182 --> 57:19.100
[man] <i>Grace.</i>
[Grace] <i>It's okay.</i>

57:19.184 --> 57:21.019
[man] <i>Grace, what is it?</i>
<i>Your nose is bleeding.</i>

57:21.144 --> 57:22.603
<i>-No, it's okay.</i>
-[man] <i>No, it's not okay.</i>

57:22.687 --> 57:24.689
<i>Look at your nose.</i>
<i>This is... Look at me.</i>

57:24.814 --> 57:26.607
<i>And the bruise. Look!</i>
<i>Did he--</i>

57:26.691 --> 57:28.901
[Grace] <i>Bradley, he just...</i>
<i>It's okay.</i>

57:29.027 --> 57:31.446
<i>Look at me, look at me.</i>
<i>He can't keep hitting you.</i>

57:31.529 --> 57:33.698
<i>-Do you understand?</i>
<i>-I know, I'm sorry.</i>

57:33.823 --> 57:36.034
[man] <i>You have nothing to be sorry for...</i>

57:40.871 --> 57:42.540
<i>All right, that's it.</i>
<i>Turn the camera--</i>

57:50.548 --> 57:52.217
[thudding]

58:21.036 --> 58:22.622
[door creaking]

59:19.011 --> 59:20.805
[curtain hook clatters]

59:32.608 --> 59:34.109
[T.J. groans]

01:00:08.060 --> 01:00:09.187
[T.J. grunts]

01:00:09.312 --> 01:00:10.855
[masked man groaning]

01:00:16.194 --> 01:00:17.820
[T.J. grunting]

01:00:23.743 --> 01:00:26.204
[whispering] I'm losing my mind.
Jesus Christ.

01:00:27.872 --> 01:00:29.039
[sighs]

01:00:31.584 --> 01:00:33.336
[urinating]

01:00:57.943 --> 01:00:58.986
[toilet flushing]

01:00:59.069 --> 01:01:01.196
[both grunting]

01:01:11.040 --> 01:01:12.708
[toilet stops flushing]

01:01:28.057 --> 01:01:29.434
[thumping]

01:01:36.774 --> 01:01:38.776
[masked men breathing heavily]

01:01:48.619 --> 01:01:50.120
-What's going on?
-Shh.

01:01:52.290 --> 01:01:53.749
Listen, I'm not sure.

01:02:10.475 --> 01:02:11.767
[clatters]

01:02:15.855 --> 01:02:17.147
[Brad] Go on.

01:02:18.649 --> 01:02:20.485
[masked man] Go, go, go.

01:02:25.155 --> 01:02:27.032
[T.J. grunting]

01:02:28.451 --> 01:02:31.912
[masked man 1] Mark, Peter.
Peter! Come on.

01:02:31.996 --> 01:02:33.122
[masked man 2] Shit!

01:02:33.205 --> 01:02:34.289
[masked man 1] No, no, no!

01:02:34.374 --> 01:02:36.000
Oh, man.
Oh, man, oh, man.

01:02:36.125 --> 01:02:38.336
Okay, okay. Oh!

01:02:38.461 --> 01:02:39.670
Okay, okay.

01:02:39.795 --> 01:02:41.589
[masked man 3 screams] Oh, God!

01:02:41.672 --> 01:02:44.133
[masked man 1]
Oh, it's okay, it's okay, it's okay.

01:02:44.216 --> 01:02:45.760
[masked man 2] What do we do?
What do we do?

01:02:45.843 --> 01:02:46.927
[masked man 1]
Take him to the hospital, Peter!

01:02:47.011 --> 01:02:48.721
-What do you think we do?
-What do you mean, the hospital?

01:02:48.846 --> 01:02:50.390
[masked man 1] Stop! Help me get him up!
Come on.

01:02:50.515 --> 01:02:51.849
[masked man 3 groans]

01:02:52.725 --> 01:02:54.810
[all grunting]

01:02:57.897 --> 01:02:59.899
[masked man 1] You got him.
You got him.

01:03:10.576 --> 01:03:11.911
[footsteps thudding]

01:03:12.036 --> 01:03:14.079
Jesus! [breathing heavily]

01:03:14.204 --> 01:03:15.498
[Travis] Our tires are slashed.

01:03:15.581 --> 01:03:17.207
-Where are Ronnie and T.J.?
-I don't know.

01:03:17.332 --> 01:03:19.710
-What do you mean you don't know?
-I mean I don't fucking know!

01:03:19.835 --> 01:03:21.086
They're not in their beds.

01:03:21.211 --> 01:03:23.255
You think that they slashed the tires?

01:03:35.017 --> 01:03:36.226
Brad?

01:03:39.397 --> 01:03:41.190
[Travis breathing heavily]

01:03:48.363 --> 01:03:49.824
[Melissa screams]

01:03:49.907 --> 01:03:51.075
[Brad] Melissa!

01:03:53.411 --> 01:03:54.412
[screaming]

01:03:55.079 --> 01:03:56.539
Ah, fuck!

01:04:02.753 --> 01:04:04.547
[Melissa panting]

01:04:06.674 --> 01:04:08.383
[screaming]

01:04:10.385 --> 01:04:12.096
[panting]

01:04:32.116 --> 01:04:34.118
[continues panting]

01:04:43.127 --> 01:04:44.545
[whimpers]

01:04:53.971 --> 01:04:55.723
[grunts]

01:04:55.806 --> 01:04:57.307
[gasping]

01:05:02.312 --> 01:05:03.981
[panting]

01:05:25.670 --> 01:05:28.088
-[T.J. grunts]
-[Melissa screams] God!

01:05:28.172 --> 01:05:29.840
[both grunting]

01:05:32.635 --> 01:05:34.512
[T.J.] No, no! [choking]

01:05:36.931 --> 01:05:37.932
[Travis] Brad!

01:05:42.687 --> 01:05:44.522
[Travis] Come here, come.
[Brad] Go, go, go!

01:05:44.647 --> 01:05:46.315
-Go! Go! Go! Come on.
-[Travis] Go, go, go.

01:05:50.194 --> 01:05:51.862
[banging on door]

01:05:56.867 --> 01:05:58.536
[Brad] Where's Melissa?
[Travis] Let's go!

01:06:06.836 --> 01:06:08.045
[gasps]

01:06:08.170 --> 01:06:09.379
[Travis stutters] Get the dresser.

01:06:22.059 --> 01:06:23.686
[Travis grunting]

01:06:27.565 --> 01:06:28.983
[Melissa] Brad?

01:06:30.651 --> 01:06:32.319
You're scaring her!

01:06:32.402 --> 01:06:33.403
[banging stops]

01:06:37.074 --> 01:06:38.993
-[EKG beeping rapidly]
-[sighs]

01:06:39.076 --> 01:06:40.745
[sighs]

01:08:03.618 --> 01:08:05.329
[breathes heavily]

01:08:10.334 --> 01:08:11.836
I'm sure he's fine.

01:08:20.803 --> 01:08:22.511
You don't trust him either.

01:08:24.098 --> 01:08:25.349
[Brad sighs]

01:08:27.350 --> 01:08:28.602
I want to.

